00:01:32.090 --> 00:01:33.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LUGNER]
Of course.</b></Default>

c0000001
00:01:34.770 --> 00:01:36.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I remember now.</b></Default>

c0000002
00:01:37.890 --> 00:01:39.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It was Frieren.</b></Default>

c0000003
00:01:41.310 --> 00:01:43.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The mage who made
great contributions</b></Default>

c0000004
00:01:43.890 --> 00:01:46.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to humanity's
analysis of Zoltraak</b></Default>

c0000005
00:01:47.030 --> 00:01:48.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and sent more demons
to the grave</b></Default>

c0000006
00:01:48.990 --> 00:01:50.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>than anyone else in history.</b></Default>

c0000007
00:01:54.190 --> 00:01:56.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Frieren the Slayer.</b></Default>

c0000008
00:01:58.200 --> 00:02:01.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>One of the geniuses
I despise.</b></Default>

c0000009
00:02:12.710 --> 00:02:15.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[PRIEST 8A] It's important that
you rest for the time being.</b></Default>

c0000010
00:02:15.220 --> 00:02:16.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I appreciate it.</b></Default>

c0000011
00:02:17.930 --> 00:02:19.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[door opens]</b></Default>

c0000012
00:02:24.600 --> 00:02:25.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Whoa, there.</b></Default>

c0000013
00:02:26.860 --> 00:02:28.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You doing okay?</b></Default>

c0000014
00:02:29.650 --> 00:02:32.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I will survive,
but only because of you two.</b></Default>

c0000015
00:02:32.730 --> 00:02:33.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GRANAT]
I'm grateful.</b></Default>

c0000016
00:02:39.040 --> 00:02:41.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll pardon your companion
for her actions as well.</b></Default>

c0000017
00:02:42.290 --> 00:02:44.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GRANAT] She was right
to take a stand when she did.</b></Default>

c0000018
00:02:46.210 --> 00:02:48.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Which means nothing's stopping
Frieren from coming back.</b></Default>

c0000019
00:02:49.420 --> 00:02:51.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The "peace" envoy's
as good as dead.</b></Default>

c0000020
00:02:52.170 --> 00:02:54.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Also...please know that
Mistress Frieren</b></Default>

c0000021
00:02:54.810 --> 00:02:56.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>didn't kill your guard.</b></Default>

c0000022
00:02:56.760 --> 00:02:57.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I am aware.</b></Default>

c0000023
00:02:58.100 --> 00:03:00.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The demons are to blame
for that, too.</b></Default>

c0000024
00:03:00.720 --> 00:03:01.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GRANAT]
More importantly,</b></Default>

c0000025
00:03:01.930 --> 00:03:04.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you said this woman's name
is Frieren?</b></Default>

c0000026
00:03:04.600 --> 00:03:05.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes.</b></Default>

c0000027
00:03:06.070 --> 00:03:08.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GRANAT] Which almost certainly
makes her the elven mage</b></Default>

c0000028
00:03:08.190 --> 00:03:09.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>who adventured with the Hero.</b></Default>

c0000029
00:03:10.770 --> 00:03:13.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've committed a grave
discourtesy against her.</b></Default>

c0000030
00:03:14.570 --> 00:03:17.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My family owes a debt
to that great band of heroes.</b></Default>

c0000031
00:03:18.080 --> 00:03:19.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GRANAT]
During my grandfather's rule,</b></Default>

c0000032
00:03:19.700 --> 00:03:21.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>this town was attacked
by demons.</b></Default>

c0000033
00:03:21.950 --> 00:03:24.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Frieren and her comrades
drove them off</b></Default>

c0000034
00:03:24.330 --> 00:03:25.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and saved our people.</b></Default>

c0000035
00:03:26.000 --> 00:03:27.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That same enemy has returned.</b></Default>

c0000036
00:03:28.130 --> 00:03:31.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Aura, one of the
Seven Sages of Destruction.</b></Default>

c0000037
00:03:33.750 --> 00:03:35.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's been a while, Aura.</b></Default>

c0000038
00:03:36.550 --> 00:03:37.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Eighty years.</b></Default>

c0000039
00:03:37.970 --> 00:03:41.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The decades fly by,
don't they, Frieren.</b></Default>

c0000040
00:03:42.300 --> 00:03:43.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000041
00:03:44.720 --> 00:03:47.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No doubt you plan to attack
the town ahead.</b></Default>

c0000042
00:03:48.360 --> 00:03:50.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] But I'd appreciate
it if you turned back now.</b></Default>

c0000043
00:03:51.440 --> 00:03:52.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[AURA]
That won't do.</b></Default>

c0000044
00:03:53.400 --> 00:03:54.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Why not?</b></Default>

c0000045
00:04:14.670 --> 00:04:18.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Because I carry an advantage
that assures my success.</b></Default>

c0000046
00:04:19.140 --> 00:04:20.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh?</b></Default>

c0000047
00:04:23.760 --> 00:04:25.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] You have
more puppets than before.</b></Default>

c0000048
00:04:26.480 --> 00:04:28.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your magic must be
unbelievably powerful</b></Default>

c0000049
00:04:28.900 --> 00:04:31.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if you're able to control
this many at once.</b></Default>

c0000050
00:04:32.150 --> 00:04:34.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm sure no human
could even begin to dream</b></Default>

c0000051
00:04:34.520 --> 00:04:36.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of wielding such might.</b></Default>

c0000052
00:04:37.570 --> 00:04:40.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But this dark magic is enough
to make me vomit.</b></Default>

c0000053
00:04:40.860 --> 00:04:42.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's disgusting.</b></Default>

c0000054
00:04:42.570 --> 00:04:44.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Vomit?
You wound me.</b></Default>

c0000055
00:04:44.830 --> 00:04:47.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It took a lot of work
to gather such an army.</b></Default>

c0000056
00:04:49.420 --> 00:04:51.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000057
00:04:56.590 --> 00:04:58.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] I recognize
some of those crests.</b></Default>

c0000058
00:05:00.340 --> 00:05:01.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Right, then.</b></Default>

c0000059
00:05:01.470 --> 00:05:04.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It seems my best option is to
kill you once and for all.</b></Default>

c0000060
00:05:05.810 --> 00:05:07.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Aura chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000061
00:05:08.690 --> 00:05:10.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GRANAT]
The Scales of Obedience.</b></Default>

c0000062
00:05:11.810 --> 00:05:14.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They're why we haven't
been able to defeat Aura</b></Default>

c0000063
00:05:14.100 --> 00:05:15.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>over the years.</b></Default>

c0000064
00:05:16.530 --> 00:05:19.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Her magic allows her to control
a person's will,</b></Default>

c0000065
00:05:19.490 --> 00:05:21.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>forces them to obey her
every command.</b></Default>

c0000066
00:05:23.780 --> 00:05:26.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The Seven Sages of Destruction
wield power</b></Default>

c0000067
00:05:26.290 --> 00:05:28.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>beyond human comprehension.</b></Default>

c0000068
00:05:28.870 --> 00:05:31.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We believe Aura places her soul</b></Default>

c0000069
00:05:31.080 --> 00:05:33.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and the soul of her target
on the scales,</b></Default>

c0000070
00:05:33.410 --> 00:05:35.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>then weighs them against
each other.</b></Default>

c0000071
00:05:36.590 --> 00:05:39.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Whoever has greater mana
gains control of the other,</b></Default>

c0000072
00:05:40.260 --> 00:05:42.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>turning them into a puppet
for all eternity,</b></Default>

c0000073
00:05:43.970 --> 00:05:46.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>until their body withers away</b></Default>

c0000074
00:05:46.430 --> 00:05:48.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and only armor remains.</b></Default>

c0000075
00:05:49.810 --> 00:05:52.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The risk involved
makes the spell powerful.</b></Default>

c0000076
00:05:53.100 --> 00:05:55.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And when it's cast by someone
as mighty as Aura,</b></Default>

c0000077
00:05:56.110 --> 00:05:57.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it cannot be overcome.</b></Default>

c0000078
00:05:58.610 --> 00:06:01.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There must be a means
of countering the spell.</b></Default>

c0000079
00:06:02.320 --> 00:06:05.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs] Aura's strength
seems unbeatable.</b></Default>

c0000080
00:06:05.620 --> 00:06:07.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GRANAT]
But the scales themselves</b></Default>

c0000081
00:06:07.160 --> 00:06:09.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>are fair, impartial judges.</b></Default>

c0000082
00:06:10.290 --> 00:06:12.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If a soul with greater mana
than Aura's</b></Default>

c0000083
00:06:12.330 --> 00:06:13.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>were to be placed upon them,</b></Default>

c0000084
00:06:14.660 --> 00:06:16.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>she could be defeated.</b></Default>

c0000085
00:06:18.420 --> 00:06:20.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Still...
according to what we know,</b></Default>

c0000086
00:06:20.800 --> 00:06:23.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that has yet to happen once
in the last 500 years,</b></Default>

c0000087
00:06:24.550 --> 00:06:27.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>ever since she became
a Sage of Destruction.</b></Default>

c0000088
00:06:27.810 --> 00:06:31.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You mean there's no way
for us to stand against her?</b></Default>

c0000089
00:06:35.530 --> 00:06:37.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Once upon a time, there was...</b></Default>

c0000090
00:06:38.940 --> 00:06:40.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GRANAT] Those with
fierce determination</b></Default>

c0000091
00:06:40.730 --> 00:06:43.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>were able to temporarily
resist Aura's spell.</b></Default>

c0000092
00:06:46.040 --> 00:06:48.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The warriors who had wills
forged of iron.</b></Default>

c0000093
00:06:49.120 --> 00:06:50.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The greatest among us.</b></Default>

c0000094
00:06:51.330 --> 00:06:53.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But even then,
it was temporary?</b></Default>

c0000095
00:06:54.080 --> 00:06:56.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Which made them
her primary targets.</b></Default>

c0000096
00:06:56.750 --> 00:06:58.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They stood in her way,</b></Default>

c0000097
00:06:58.670 --> 00:07:00.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>threatened her victory.</b></Default>

c0000098
00:07:00.710 --> 00:07:01.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And so,</b></Default>

c0000099
00:07:03.750 --> 00:07:05.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>when she finally broke them,</b></Default>

c0000100
00:07:05.970 --> 00:07:07.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Aura the Guillotine
made certain</b></Default>

c0000101
00:07:07.720 --> 00:07:09.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>they would no longer
pose a threat to her.</b></Default>

c0000102
00:07:11.010 --> 00:07:12.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GRANAT]
It's a tragic tale.</b></Default>

c0000103
00:07:19.020 --> 00:07:20.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[AURA]
Well?</b></Default>

c0000104
00:07:20.610 --> 00:07:23.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Haven't I impressed you
with my immortal soldiers?</b></Default>

c0000105
00:07:38.210 --> 00:07:40.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My, this is a surprise.</b></Default>

c0000106
00:07:40.540 --> 00:07:43.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[AURA] You dispelled the magic
I used to control them.</b></Default>

c0000107
00:07:43.880 --> 00:07:46.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No one's ever done that before.</b></Default>

c0000108
00:07:46.850 --> 00:07:48.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Such a formidable act
must consume</b></Default>

c0000109
00:07:48.890 --> 00:07:50.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a monumental amount
of mana, though,</b></Default>

c0000110
00:07:51.180 --> 00:07:53.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>leaving you exhausted.</b></Default>

c0000111
00:07:54.010 --> 00:07:56.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why would you use
such a roundabout method?</b></Default>

c0000112
00:07:58.360 --> 00:07:59.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The last time you faced me,</b></Default>

c0000113
00:07:59.900 --> 00:08:02.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you were casting flashy spells
left and right.</b></Default>

c0000114
00:08:04.980 --> 00:08:07.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] Himmel scolded me
after that battle.</b></Default>

c0000115
00:08:08.570 --> 00:08:10.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[AURA]
You're holding back for him?</b></Default>

c0000116
00:08:10.280 --> 00:08:12.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't see why his words
should matter to you.</b></Default>

c0000117
00:08:14.070 --> 00:08:15.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Why wouldn't they?</b></Default>

c0000118
00:08:15.830 --> 00:08:17.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Because Himmel is rotting
in the ground.</b></Default>

c0000119
00:08:20.040 --> 00:08:21.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Thank you for saying that.</b></Default>

c0000120
00:08:24.000 --> 00:08:26.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You've reminded me that
demons are just monsters.</b></Default>

c0000121
00:08:27.300 --> 00:08:29.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So I can kill you
without mercy.</b></Default>

c0000122
00:08:29.890 --> 00:08:31.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
All right.</b></Default>

c0000123
00:08:31.890 --> 00:08:34.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've regained
most of my mobility.</b></Default>

c0000124
00:08:35.650 --> 00:08:38.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK] Father,
this place is safe, right?</b></Default>

c0000125
00:08:38.770 --> 00:08:39.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes.</b></Default>

c0000126
00:08:40.100 --> 00:08:42.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's a defensive barrier
around the church,</b></Default>

c0000127
00:08:42.650 --> 00:08:45.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>though it's not as powerful
as the town's, I'm afraid.</b></Default>

c0000128
00:08:46.110 --> 00:08:48.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK] Got it.
Graf, you wait here.</b></Default>

c0000129
00:08:49.320 --> 00:08:50.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Not so fast.</b></Default>

c0000130
00:08:50.780 --> 00:08:52.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GRANAT]
What do you plan to do, brat?</b></Default>

c0000131
00:08:53.160 --> 00:08:54.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
We may have escaped the demons,</b></Default>

c0000132
00:08:54.990 --> 00:08:57.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but they're still out there
plotting somewhere.</b></Default>

c0000133
00:08:57.620 --> 00:08:58.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
Mister Stark.</b></Default>

c0000134
00:08:59.080 --> 00:09:00.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Be reasonable.</b></Default>

c0000135
00:09:01.080 --> 00:09:02.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] We only injured
that demon before</b></Default>

c0000136
00:09:03.040 --> 00:09:04.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>because we took him
by surprise.</b></Default>

c0000137
00:09:05.380 --> 00:09:08.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Even with that advantage,
we couldn't finish him off.</b></Default>

c0000138
00:09:09.590 --> 00:09:11.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If we had kept
fighting those two,</b></Default>

c0000139
00:09:11.880 --> 00:09:13.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we would have been the ones
who were killed.</b></Default>

c0000140
00:09:15.520 --> 00:09:17.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK] Someone's gotta
step up and try to stop them.</b></Default>

c0000141
00:09:20.350 --> 00:09:21.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But...</b></Default>

c0000142
00:09:23.520 --> 00:09:24.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
You're right.</b></Default>

c0000143
00:09:25.110 --> 00:09:26.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let me do this with you.</b></Default>

c0000144
00:09:28.780 --> 00:09:29.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
No.</b></Default>

c0000145
00:09:30.240 --> 00:09:31.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You need to head
to the guard station.</b></Default>

c0000146
00:09:32.490 --> 00:09:34.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Start evacuating the townsfolk.</b></Default>

c0000147
00:09:35.370 --> 00:09:36.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You'll go out there alone?</b></Default>

c0000148
00:09:39.620 --> 00:09:40.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
Yeah.</b></Default>

c0000149
00:09:41.250 --> 00:09:42.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No sweat.</b></Default>

c0000150
00:09:43.000 --> 00:09:45.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll swallow my pride
and beg Frieren to return.</b></Default>

c0000151
00:09:47.800 --> 00:09:48.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
Huh?</b></Default>

c0000152
00:09:51.050 --> 00:09:52.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK] She's obviously
the only person around</b></Default>

c0000153
00:09:52.880 --> 00:09:54.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>who can defeat Lugner!</b></Default>

c0000154
00:09:55.350 --> 00:09:57.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
Not what I was expecting,</b></Default>

c0000155
00:09:57.230 --> 00:09:58.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but more realistic.</b></Default>

c0000156
00:10:03.230 --> 00:10:05.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK] Here.
The guards will listen to you</b></Default>

c0000157
00:10:05.320 --> 00:10:06.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if you show them this crest.</b></Default>

c0000158
00:10:08.030 --> 00:10:09.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
Very well.</b></Default>

c0000159
00:10:10.650 --> 00:10:11.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
I'm heading out of town.</b></Default>

c0000160
00:10:14.240 --> 00:10:15.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What is it?</b></Default>

c0000161
00:10:15.540 --> 00:10:16.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your arm.</b></Default>

c0000162
00:10:16.660 --> 00:10:18.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's all covered in blood.</b></Default>

c0000163
00:10:19.160 --> 00:10:21.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're not worried they'll
question you at the gate?</b></Default>

c0000164
00:10:23.000 --> 00:10:24.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
I'll be fine.</b></Default>

c0000165
00:10:24.540 --> 00:10:26.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Comes with being a warrior.</b></Default>

c0000166
00:10:26.550 --> 00:10:28.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Plus, it's not that much.</b></Default>

c0000167
00:10:28.800 --> 00:10:30.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've never seen a warrior
walk through town</b></Default>

c0000168
00:10:30.840 --> 00:10:32.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with two bloody hands.</b></Default>

c0000169
00:10:32.170 --> 00:10:33.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You look like a murderer.</b></Default>

c0000170
00:10:34.170 --> 00:10:35.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
You're one to talk.</b></Default>

c0000171
00:10:35.680 --> 00:10:37.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You've got just as much on you
as I do.</b></Default>

c0000172
00:10:37.720 --> 00:10:38.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000173
00:10:39.810 --> 00:10:41.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wait.
Whose blood is this?</b></Default>

c0000174
00:10:41.390 --> 00:10:42.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It couldn't be mine.</b></Default>

c0000175
00:10:45.940 --> 00:10:47.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
Hey!</b></Default>

c0000176
00:10:47.530 --> 00:10:49.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What is the matter with you?</b></Default>

c0000177
00:10:52.980 --> 00:10:55.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] Mister Stark,
there's mana in this blood!</b></Default>

c0000178
00:10:57.240 --> 00:10:58.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
Fern!</b></Default>

c0000179
00:11:07.000 --> 00:11:08.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
An axe?</b></Default>

c0000180
00:11:13.210 --> 00:11:14.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Unbelievable.</b></Default>

c0000181
00:11:14.670 --> 00:11:16.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've got to be dreaming
or something.</b></Default>

c0000182
00:11:17.510 --> 00:11:20.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK] 'Cause that looked
like my master's technique.</b></Default>

c0000183
00:11:23.560 --> 00:11:25.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LUGNER]
I meant to hit your vitals,</b></Default>

c0000184
00:11:25.100 --> 00:11:27.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but you're faster
than I expected.</b></Default>

c0000185
00:11:28.230 --> 00:11:31.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It truly wasn't my intention
to make you suffer.</b></Default>

c0000186
00:11:35.740 --> 00:11:37.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why do you look so shocked?</b></Default>

c0000187
00:11:38.200 --> 00:11:40.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did you think your attack
had killed me?</b></Default>

c0000188
00:11:40.200 --> 00:11:42.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That I was mortally wounded?</b></Default>

c0000189
00:11:42.620 --> 00:11:44.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LUGNER]
No. You're surprised</b></Default>

c0000190
00:11:44.370 --> 00:11:46.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you didn't sense us
as we approached.</b></Default>

c0000191
00:11:48.460 --> 00:11:50.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You aren't unique
in your ability</b></Default>

c0000192
00:11:50.130 --> 00:11:51.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to conceal your presence.</b></Default>

c0000193
00:11:51.920 --> 00:11:54.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's a simple matter
of controlling one's mana.</b></Default>

c0000194
00:11:54.840 --> 00:11:56.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LUGNER]
Any demon can do the same,</b></Default>

c0000195
00:11:56.510 --> 00:11:57.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>should they wish.</b></Default>

c0000196
00:11:58.760 --> 00:11:59.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>To be fair,</b></Default>

c0000197
00:12:00.180 --> 00:12:01.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it's hardly a noble way</b></Default>

c0000198
00:12:01.640 --> 00:12:03.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to approach a battle
between two mages.</b></Default>

c0000199
00:12:03.930 --> 00:12:05.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But these things happen.</b></Default>

c0000200
00:12:06.650 --> 00:12:08.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You like to hear yourself talk.</b></Default>

c0000201
00:12:08.900 --> 00:12:10.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Didn't you come here
to kill me?</b></Default>

c0000202
00:12:12.230 --> 00:12:14.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>True. But seeing
as you're still alive,</b></Default>

c0000203
00:12:14.310 --> 00:12:16.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I might as well ask
a few questions.</b></Default>

c0000204
00:12:18.570 --> 00:12:20.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Unless, of course,
you're in a hurry to die.</b></Default>

c0000205
00:12:22.780 --> 00:12:23.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Go on.</b></Default>

c0000206
00:12:26.750 --> 00:12:28.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LUGNER]
How strong is that boy?</b></Default>

c0000207
00:12:29.790 --> 00:12:32.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] He's Eisen the Warrior's
best student.</b></Default>

c0000208
00:12:32.750 --> 00:12:33.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LUGNER]
I see.</b></Default>

c0000209
00:12:34.130 --> 00:12:35.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How unfortunate.</b></Default>

c0000210
00:12:36.180 --> 00:12:38.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The poor thing will die
a torturous death.</b></Default>

c0000211
00:12:38.680 --> 00:12:40.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Linie likes to take her time.</b></Default>

c0000212
00:12:43.510 --> 00:12:44.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>One last thing.</b></Default>

c0000213
00:12:45.400 --> 00:12:47.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Where is Frieren hiding?</b></Default>

c0000214
00:12:50.100 --> 00:12:52.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She fled town after escaping.</b></Default>

c0000215
00:12:53.060 --> 00:12:54.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
She had to,</b></Default>

c0000216
00:12:54.310 --> 00:12:56.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>because you killed
the dungeon guard.</b></Default>

c0000217
00:12:57.030 --> 00:12:59.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Graf Granat blamed me
for that, as well.</b></Default>

c0000218
00:12:59.820 --> 00:13:02.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is it really
such a serious offense?</b></Default>

c0000219
00:13:02.950 --> 00:13:04.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The penalty's death.</b></Default>

c0000220
00:13:04.700 --> 00:13:05.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LUGNER]
Hm.</b></Default>

c0000221
00:13:06.170 --> 00:13:08.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Still, a woman like Frieren
wouldn't flee</b></Default>

c0000222
00:13:08.460 --> 00:13:09.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>because of such a danger.</b></Default>

c0000223
00:13:10.460 --> 00:13:13.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's obvious she holds
a grudge against demons.</b></Default>

c0000224
00:13:14.210 --> 00:13:16.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>One so spiteful,
she taught her student</b></Default>

c0000225
00:13:16.300 --> 00:13:18.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a spell designed
solely to kill us.</b></Default>

c0000226
00:13:20.340 --> 00:13:22.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No. She would not run away.</b></Default>

c0000227
00:13:23.380 --> 00:13:25.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She left for another reason.</b></Default>

c0000228
00:13:28.480 --> 00:13:29.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>For Lady Aura.</b></Default>

c0000229
00:13:33.690 --> 00:13:35.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do not take another step.</b></Default>

c0000230
00:13:36.570 --> 00:13:39.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] I suspect you know
exactly where she's headed.</b></Default>

c0000231
00:13:39.280 --> 00:13:40.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Explain.</b></Default>

c0000232
00:13:41.150 --> 00:13:42.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LUGNER]
You're wasting your time.</b></Default>

c0000233
00:13:43.780 --> 00:13:44.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You were lying when you said</b></Default>

c0000234
00:13:44.990 --> 00:13:47.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>your intent wasn't for me
to suffer.</b></Default>

c0000235
00:13:47.620 --> 00:13:49.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] That attack
was never meant to kill me.</b></Default>

c0000236
00:13:50.080 --> 00:13:52.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It was revenge
for catching you off guard.</b></Default>

c0000237
00:13:53.290 --> 00:13:55.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You are a proud
and arrogant demon,</b></Default>

c0000238
00:13:55.970 --> 00:13:57.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so sure of your strength</b></Default>

c0000239
00:13:58.050 --> 00:14:01.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that you see Mistress Frieren
as the only threat in your way.</b></Default>

c0000240
00:14:02.260 --> 00:14:03.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
Underestimating me</b></Default>

c0000241
00:14:03.470 --> 00:14:05.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>has put you in
a dire predicament.</b></Default>

c0000242
00:14:07.810 --> 00:14:09.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>From this distance,</b></Default>

c0000243
00:14:09.140 --> 00:14:11.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can blast a hole
clean through your heart.</b></Default>

c0000244
00:14:12.890 --> 00:14:14.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LUGNER]
Try it.</b></Default>

c0000245
00:14:14.480 --> 00:14:16.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your head will fly
before you get the chance.</b></Default>

c0000246
00:14:25.150 --> 00:14:26.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
Mistress Frieren?</b></Default>

c0000247
00:14:27.450 --> 00:14:29.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Am I of any real use to you?</b></Default>

c0000248
00:14:30.080 --> 00:14:31.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Why would you ask such a thing?</b></Default>

c0000249
00:14:33.370 --> 00:14:35.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN] I'm not as skilled
with magic as you are.</b></Default>

c0000250
00:14:36.380 --> 00:14:38.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's more than apparent.</b></Default>

c0000251
00:14:39.300 --> 00:14:42.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] I've lived many,
many more years than you have.</b></Default>

c0000252
00:14:42.670 --> 00:14:44.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You can't hope
to catch up to me.</b></Default>

c0000253
00:14:47.060 --> 00:14:48.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FERN]
I see.</b></Default>

c0000254
00:14:49.020 --> 00:14:51.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Of course, that only applies
to your technique</b></Default>

c0000255
00:14:51.470 --> 00:14:52.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and your mana reserves.</b></Default>

c0000256
00:14:53.810 --> 00:14:55.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] I often
let you handle monsters.</b></Default>

c0000257
00:14:55.730 --> 00:14:57.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You prove yourself
in those battles.</b></Default>

c0000258
00:14:57.690 --> 00:15:00.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes. You force me
to fight them often.</b></Default>

c0000259
00:15:00.570 --> 00:15:02.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN]
Apologies.</b></Default>

c0000260
00:15:02.730 --> 00:15:05.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Battles end sooner
whenever you fight by my side.</b></Default>

c0000261
00:15:06.370 --> 00:15:08.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You fire off spells
much faster than I do.</b></Default>

c0000262
00:15:11.540 --> 00:15:12.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LUGNER]
Human...</b></Default>

c0000263
00:15:13.450 --> 00:15:15.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've dedicated
the majority of my life</b></Default>

c0000264
00:15:15.670 --> 00:15:17.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to the pursuit of magic.</b></Default>

c0000265
00:15:18.170 --> 00:15:19.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>As have I.</b></Default>

c0000266
00:15:28.850 --> 00:15:29.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000267
00:15:34.100 --> 00:15:36.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LUGNER] How is she responding
so quickly?</b></Default>

c0000268
00:15:37.110 --> 00:15:39.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If I hadn't acted reflexively,</b></Default>

c0000269
00:15:39.730 --> 00:15:41.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that would've pierced my heart.</b></Default>

c0000270
00:15:42.110 --> 00:15:43.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You blocked my attack,</b></Default>

c0000271
00:15:44.070 --> 00:15:46.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>which must mean your heart
is your weak point.</b></Default>

c0000272
00:15:47.370 --> 00:15:48.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LUGNER]
This girl.</b></Default>

c0000273
00:15:50.160 --> 00:15:51.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Interesting.</b></Default>

c0000274
00:15:51.780 --> 00:15:54.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You weren't lying about
dedicating your life to magic.</b></Default>

c0000275
00:15:56.420 --> 00:15:59.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's good. I won't need
to hold back in this fight.</b></Default>

c0000276
00:16:00.290 --> 00:16:01.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LUGNER] Bluterei!</b></Default>

c0000277
00:16:04.750 --> 00:16:06.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It sounds like
they've gotten started.</b></Default>

c0000278
00:16:08.470 --> 00:16:10.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That makes me
a little bit jealous.</b></Default>

c0000279
00:16:10.850 --> 00:16:12.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LINIE]
Our fight is all but over.</b></Default>

c0000280
00:16:14.220 --> 00:16:16.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Perhaps
I'll observe their battle</b></Default>

c0000281
00:16:16.360 --> 00:16:17.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>from afar.</b></Default>

c0000282
00:16:18.190 --> 00:16:20.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Lord Lugner gets cross
when I interfere.</b></Default>

c0000283
00:16:23.150 --> 00:16:24.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Stark groans]</b></Default>

c0000284
00:16:25.870 --> 00:16:26.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LINIE]
You're up?</b></Default>

c0000285
00:16:26.950 --> 00:16:29.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But we're not finished yet!</b></Default>

c0000286
00:16:30.910 --> 00:16:32.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LINIE]
Aren't you tough?</b></Default>

c0000287
00:16:32.320 --> 00:16:34.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Perhaps this will be amusing.</b></Default>

c0000288
00:16:38.130 --> 00:16:40.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LUGNER] My mana, technique,
and control</b></Default>

c0000289
00:16:40.710 --> 00:16:43.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>are all far superior to hers.</b></Default>

c0000290
00:16:45.080 --> 00:16:47.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000291
00:17:03.560 --> 00:17:06.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LUGNER] She can't compare
to me in any way.</b></Default>

c0000292
00:17:06.240 --> 00:17:08.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The very thought of it
is ridiculous.</b></Default>

c0000293
00:17:09.450 --> 00:17:12.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>However, she is fast.</b></Default>

c0000294
00:17:13.410 --> 00:17:14.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm being overwhelmed</b></Default>

c0000295
00:17:14.700 --> 00:17:17.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>by the sheer number
of her attacks.</b></Default>

c0000296
00:17:18.170 --> 00:17:19.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000297
00:17:22.750 --> 00:17:24.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LUGNER]
Damn you, Frieren.</b></Default>

c0000298
00:17:24.790 --> 00:17:27.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How did you train this girl
to put up such a fight?</b></Default>

c0000299
00:17:31.680 --> 00:17:32.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's no matter.</b></Default>

c0000300
00:17:33.090 --> 00:17:35.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She'll exhaust her mana soon.</b></Default>

c0000301
00:17:48.360 --> 00:17:49.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>On second thought,</b></Default>

c0000302
00:17:50.490 --> 00:17:52.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm not sure
I can wait her out.</b></Default>

c0000303
00:17:53.700 --> 00:17:55.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If I can just create
an opening.</b></Default>

c0000304
00:17:57.370 --> 00:17:59.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Linie, quit playing around.</b></Default>

c0000305
00:17:59.410 --> 00:18:01.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hurry up and kill that boy!</b></Default>

c0000306
00:18:04.040 --> 00:18:05.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[groans]</b></Default>

c0000307
00:18:08.050 --> 00:18:10.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The human wants
to deny me my fun.</b></Default>

c0000308
00:18:10.420 --> 00:18:13.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He's refusing to do anything
but defend himself.</b></Default>

c0000309
00:18:17.890 --> 00:18:19.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[groans]</b></Default>

c0000310
00:18:31.940 --> 00:18:34.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't understand
the way you're fighting.</b></Default>

c0000311
00:18:35.240 --> 00:18:37.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your technique
is like my master's.</b></Default>

c0000312
00:18:38.080 --> 00:18:40.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm exceptional at reading
the mana in other people.</b></Default>

c0000313
00:18:42.120 --> 00:18:43.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My specialty is memorizing
the way</b></Default>

c0000314
00:18:43.830 --> 00:18:46.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it flows inside of a person
as they move,</b></Default>

c0000315
00:18:46.460 --> 00:18:48.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>which allows me
to imitate them.</b></Default>

c0000316
00:18:48.630 --> 00:18:50.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just like this.</b></Default>

c0000317
00:18:54.210 --> 00:18:55.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[groans]</b></Default>

c0000318
00:19:14.070 --> 00:19:15.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I recognized your technique</b></Default>

c0000319
00:19:15.610 --> 00:19:18.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the moment you attacked us
at the mansion.</b></Default>

c0000320
00:19:18.540 --> 00:19:20.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LINIE] Because I memorized it
years ago</b></Default>

c0000321
00:19:20.990 --> 00:19:23.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>as I watched
a great warrior fight.</b></Default>

c0000322
00:19:27.000 --> 00:19:28.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What an odd coincidence.</b></Default>

c0000323
00:19:29.090 --> 00:19:30.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Fate is a funny thing.</b></Default>

c0000324
00:19:31.300 --> 00:19:32.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[groans]</b></Default>

c0000325
00:19:35.210 --> 00:19:36.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You mean...</b></Default>

c0000326
00:19:36.810 --> 00:19:38.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm going to take your life</b></Default>

c0000327
00:19:38.180 --> 00:19:40.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>using Eisen the Warrior's
movements.</b></Default>

c0000328
00:19:41.640 --> 00:19:44.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK] If I am dreaming,
then this is a nightmare.</b></Default>

c0000329
00:19:47.320 --> 00:19:49.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can't win against her.</b></Default>

c0000330
00:19:50.020 --> 00:19:51.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Stark groans]</b></Default>

c0000331
00:19:58.330 --> 00:19:59.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There. He's finally fallen.</b></Default>

c0000332
00:20:00.450 --> 00:20:01.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I should go back.</b></Default>

c0000333
00:20:02.160 --> 00:20:04.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't want to upset
Lord Lugner.</b></Default>

c0000334
00:20:07.750 --> 00:20:08.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
Is that it?</b></Default>

c0000335
00:20:10.290 --> 00:20:12.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is this how it ends?</b></Default>

c0000336
00:20:16.260 --> 00:20:17.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[EISEN]
Stand up, Stark.</b></Default>

c0000337
00:20:18.050 --> 00:20:19.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Find the strength.</b></Default>

c0000338
00:20:19.600 --> 00:20:22.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No matter how battered you get,
you cannot fall.</b></Default>

c0000339
00:20:23.600 --> 00:20:26.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK] Why do we keep
sparring like this?</b></Default>

c0000340
00:20:27.190 --> 00:20:29.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No matter how hard I try,
I'm not going to beat you.</b></Default>

c0000341
00:20:30.650 --> 00:20:31.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[EISEN]
Of course not.</b></Default>

c0000342
00:20:31.980 --> 00:20:34.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm far stronger than you are.</b></Default>

c0000343
00:20:35.360 --> 00:20:36.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
Then what's the point?</b></Default>

c0000344
00:20:37.120 --> 00:20:38.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[EISEN]
Look at you.</b></Default>

c0000345
00:20:38.240 --> 00:20:40.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're back on your feet,
aren't you?</b></Default>

c0000346
00:20:40.570 --> 00:20:42.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You haven't lost yet.</b></Default>

c0000347
00:20:43.620 --> 00:20:45.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That makes no sense.</b></Default>

c0000348
00:20:45.700 --> 00:20:47.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[EISEN]
Listen, Stark.</b></Default>

c0000349
00:20:47.460 --> 00:20:48.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll teach you the secret</b></Default>

c0000350
00:20:48.670 --> 00:20:50.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to defeating
powerful opponents.</b></Default>

c0000351
00:20:51.710 --> 00:20:52.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's simple.</b></Default>

c0000352
00:20:53.080 --> 00:20:55.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All you have to do is
keep getting back up</b></Default>

c0000353
00:20:55.130 --> 00:20:56.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and hitting your enemy.</b></Default>

c0000354
00:20:56.680 --> 00:20:57.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Understand?</b></Default>

c0000355
00:20:58.430 --> 00:21:00.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The winner is the warrior</b></Default>

c0000356
00:21:00.590 --> 00:21:02.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>who's still on their feet
at the end.</b></Default>

c0000357
00:21:06.100 --> 00:21:08.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK] You talked like
it was so easy, Master.</b></Default>

c0000358
00:21:09.560 --> 00:21:11.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You and your crazy logic.</b></Default>

c0000359
00:21:12.270 --> 00:21:14.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You shoulda trained your brain
as much as your body.</b></Default>

c0000360
00:21:15.270 --> 00:21:16.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Linie sighs]</b></Default>

c0000361
00:21:16.910 --> 00:21:19.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A smarter person
would have stayed in the dirt.</b></Default>

c0000362
00:21:19.780 --> 00:21:21.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've already defeated you.</b></Default>

c0000363
00:21:22.280 --> 00:21:24.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yet here I am, still standing.</b></Default>

c0000364
00:21:26.370 --> 00:21:28.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK] You know,
now I think about it,</b></Default>

c0000365
00:21:28.750 --> 00:21:31.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>my master's blows
were heavier than yours.</b></Default>

c0000366
00:21:32.620 --> 00:21:35.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're just the poor imitation
of a great warrior.</b></Default>

c0000367
00:21:40.720 --> 00:21:42.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LINIE]
Imitation or not,</b></Default>

c0000368
00:21:42.550 --> 00:21:44.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll still be the death of you.</b></Default>

c0000369
00:21:45.430 --> 00:21:46.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Erfassen.</b></Default>

c0000370
00:21:47.100 --> 00:21:48.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Bluterei!</b></Default>

c0000371
00:22:01.150 --> 00:22:02.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LINIE]
Wide swing.</b></Default>

c0000372
00:22:02.820 --> 00:22:06.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>With no regard for defense.
Idiot.</b></Default>

c0000373
00:22:12.540 --> 00:22:13.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When I saw how you fought,</b></Default>

c0000374
00:22:14.000 --> 00:22:16.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was prepared for us both
to kill each other.</b></Default>

c0000375
00:22:16.630 --> 00:22:19.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But your attacks don't have
any weight behind them.</b></Default>

c0000376
00:22:21.760 --> 00:22:23.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[STARK]
Lightning Strike!</b></Default>

c0000377
00:22:23.590 --> 00:22:24.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000378
00:22:35.140 --> 00:22:37.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Linie! Shit.</b></Default>

c0000379
00:22:37.320 --> 00:22:38.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Zoltraak.</b></Default>

c0000380
00:22:43.570 --> 00:22:46.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[LUGNER]
Magic designed to kill demons.</b></Default>

c0000381
00:24:20.380 --> 00:24:23.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[HEITER] It appears she has
roughly one-fifth of my mana.</b></Default>

c0000382
00:24:23.500 --> 00:24:25.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[AURA] You are absolutely
no match for me.</b></Default>

c0000383
00:24:26.350 --> 00:24:27.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FRIEREN] The truth is,</b></Default>

c0000384
00:24:27.430 --> 00:24:30.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you are far more powerful
a mage than I am.</b></Default>

